   <Vertical id="Introduction">
       <Markdown>
            # Writing Process Journal 1
            **Frequency of Past Writing Experiences**
            
            Think about how often you do various kinds of writing.
            The next several screens ask you to estimate how often you write each type.
       </Markdown>
   </Vertical>
   <Vertical id="Step 1">
       <Markdown>
