         cols: Daily, Weekly, Monthly, Every Semester, Rarely or Never
         rows: Fiction (including drama and fan fiction and graphic novels), A list (e.g. to do list or grocery list), An essay, A text message or direct message, An annotated bibliography
       </TabularMCQ>
       <Markdown>
         Select one option for each row. Your selections are automatically saved.
       </Markdown>
